VideoNote Notice
================

VideoNote is developed as a customized video note workspace.

This repository includes work derived from the open-source BiliNote project by
Jeffery Huang, licensed under the MIT License. The original MIT copyright
notice is preserved in LICENSE as required by the license.

Major custom work in this repository includes product rebranding, workflow
adjustments, screenshot selection and visual enhancement logic, frontend user
experience changes, and local deployment refinements.
